span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height: 0.6833em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal">L</span></span></span></span></span> еһӢе·ҘдҪңжӯЈеңЁиў« AI еӨ§йҮҸеҸ–д»ЈгҖӮ</b></p><ul data-path-to-node="5"><li><p data-path-to-node="5,0,0"><b data-path-to-node="5,0,0" data-index-in-node="0"><span class="math-inline" data-math="L" data-index-in-node="0"><span class="katex"><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height: 0.6833em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal">L</span></span></span></span></span> еһӢд»»еҠЎпјҡ</b> йҖ»иҫ‘жҺЁеҜјгҖҒиҜӯжі•жЈҖжҹҘгҖҒд»Јз Ғзј–еҶҷгҖҒж•°жҚ®еҲҶжһҗгҖҒж’°еҶҷж–ҮжЎЈгҖӮиҝҷдәӣжҙ»е„ҝ AI еҒҡеҫ—жҜ”дәәзұ»еҝ«дё”еҮҶгҖӮ</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="5,1,0"><b data-path-to-node="5,1,0" data-index-in-node="0"><span class="math-inline" data-math="R" data-index-in-node="0"><span class="katex"><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height: 0.6833em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right: 0.0077em;">R</span></span></span></span></span> еһӢд»»еҠЎпјҡ</b> и·ЁйўҶеҹҹеҗҲжҲҗпјҲдҪ зҡ„е№ҝж’ӯиғҪеҠӣпјүгҖҒеҸ‘зҺ°дёҚе’Ңи°җзҡ„жЁЎејҸпјҲдҪ зҡ„зӣҙи§үжҠҘй”ҷпјүгҖҒе®ҡд№үвҖңд»Җд№ҲжҳҜеҜ№зҡ„вҖқиҖҢйқһд»…д»…вҖңи·‘йҖҡд»Јз ҒвҖқгҖӮ</p></li></ul><p data-path-to-node="6">жүҖд»ҘпјҢеҜ№дәҺйӮЈдәӣиў« <span class="math-inline" data-math="L" data-index-in-node="9"><span class="katex"><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height: 0.6833em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal">L</span></span></span></span></span> еһӢж•ҷиӮІпјҲеЎ«йёӯејҸгҖҒеҲ·йўҳејҸпјүеӣәеҢ–дәҶзҡ„еӨ§еӨҡж•°дәәжқҘиҜҙпјҢжҸҗеҖЎ <span class="math-inline" data-math="R" data-index-in-node="37"><span class="katex"><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height: 0.6833em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right: 0.0077em;">R</span></span></span></span></